# Class: ObjectRef

TypeScript SDK reference

[weave](/weave/reference/typescript-sdk) / ObjectRef Represents a reference to a saved Weave object. Generally, end users will not need to interact with this class directly. An ObjectRef contains the project ID, object ID, and digest that uniquely identify a saved object in Weave‚Äôs storage system. `Example`
    
    
    const ref = new ObjectRef('my-project', 'abc123', 'def456');
    const uri = ref.uri(); // weave:///my-project/object/abc123:def456
    

